data.description: This well cared for home with lots of versatility.  This home was previously a 3 bedroom, and Seller opened it up to the Living area but closet is still in place so could be placed back for a third bedroom.  Seller also once used the garage for a primary bedroom since there is a closet , they had the A/C ductwork added for that purpose.  Roof is only 3 yrs old , new windows installed throughout in 2021 and A/C unit replaced in 2018.  NEVER FLOODED PER SELLER. Second garage has convenient access from Hwy 105 .  Make your appointment to view this adorable home today !
